The survey data are collected for the Bureau of Labor Statistics by the U.S. Census Bureau.The CE collects information on all spending components including food, housing, apparel and services, transportation, entertainment, and out-of-pocket health care costs including insurance premiums.</dct:description>         <dcat:keyword>community-health</dcat:keyword>
